text: Ebonshire - Volume 5 is the 26th album released by Nox Arcana. It is the fifth in a series of winter holiday EPs inspired by Nox Arcana's holiday music trilogy: Winter's Knight (2005), Winter's Eve (2009), and Winter's Majesty (2012), which are each set in a fantasy realm called Ebonshire. ==Track listing== # Solstice Eve – 3:30 # Candles In The Snow – 3:03 # Winter Spell – 4:13 # Stars In The Heavens – 4:00 == References == == External links == * Category:Nox Arcana albums Category:2017 Christmas albums Category:Christmas EPs Category:Christmas albums by American artists Category:New-age Christmas albums
